      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier, export_text\n",
        "from math import log2\n",
        "\n",
        "# Function to calculate entropy\n",
        "def calculate_entropy(data):\n",
        "    labels, counts = np.unique(data, return_counts=True)\n",
        "    probabilities = counts / counts.sum()\n",
        "    entropy = -np.sum(probabilities * np.log2(probabilities))\n",
        "    return entropy\n",
        "\n",
        "# Function to calculate information gain\n",
        "def calculate_information_gain(data, feature_column, target_column):\n",
        "    total_entropy = calculate_entropy(data[target_column])\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Calculate weighted entropy for the split\n",
        "    values, counts = np.unique(data[feature_column], return_counts=True)\n",
        "    weighted_entropy = 0\n",
        "    for i, value in enumerate(values):\n",
        "        subset = data[data[feature_column] == value]\n",
        "        subset_entropy = calculate_entropy(subset[target_column])\n",
        "        weighted_entropy += (counts[i] / counts.sum()) * subset_entropy\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Information gain is the difference\n",
        "    information_gain = total_entropy - weighted_entropy\n",
        "    return information_gain\n",
        "\n",
        "# Load data from CSV\n",
        "file_path = input(\"Enter the path to your CSV file: \")\n",
        "df = pd.read_csv(file_path)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Specify target column\n",
        "target_column = input(\"Enter the name of the target column: \")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Select features (exclude the target column)\n",
        "features = [col for col in df.columns if col != target_column]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Calculate information gain for each feature\n",
        "gains = {}\n",
        "for feature in features:\n",
        "    gains[feature] = calculate_information_gain(df, feature, target_column)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Display information gains\n",
        "print(\"Information Gain for each feature:\")\n",
        "for feature, gain in gains.items():\n",
        "    print(f\"{feature}: {gain:.4f}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Build and visualize the decision tree using sklearn\n",
        "decision_tree = DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion='entropy')\n",
        "X = df[features]\n",
        "X = pd.get_dummies(X, drop_first=True)  # Convert categorical variables to dummy/indicator variables\n",
        "y = df[target_column]\n",
        "decision_tree.fit(X, y)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Visualize the decision tree\n",
        "print(\"\\nDecision Tree:\")\n",
        "tree_rules = export_text(decision_tree, feature_names=list(X.columns))\n",
        "print(tree_rules)"
      ]
    },
